
<div class="parallax_scrolling">
    <div class="dark_background">

        <!--Title Stuff-->

        <header class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4 col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-3 col-xs-8 col-xs-offset-2">
                <p class="oxygen" id="home-logo">
                    Canberra Restaurants
                </p>
            </div>
        </header>
        <header class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1">
                <p class="lato">"One cannot think well, love well, sleep well, if one has not dined well."</p>
                <p class="niconne" id="quote-author">Virginia Woolf</p>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!--Welcome Stuff-->

        <section class="row row-white">
            <div class="col-md-5 col-md-offset-1 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                <p class="niconne niconne-row">Welcome To</p>
                <p class="oxygen oxygen-row">Canberra Restaurants</p>
                <p class="text-black">At Canberra Restaurants, we provide an overview of restaurants within Canberra and allow you to find a meal based on a certain cuisine, a specific dish that you're after or you're just after a meal within price range.</p>
                <p class="text-black" style="padding-bottom: 50px">We've got it all here for you. Just scroll down for further information.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                <div class="row" style="padding-bottom: 50px;">
                    <div class="col-sm-6 col-xs-6">
                        <img src="~/images/foodimg4.jpg" class="welcome-image" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-6 col-xs-6">
                        <img src="~/images/foodimg3.jpg" class="welcome-image" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!--Info Stuff-->

        <section class="row" style="padding: 0 25px 0 25px;">
            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                <h2 class="niconne niconne-centre">Cuisine</h2>
                <p class="text-white">The multicultural society in Canberra spoils the locals with such a vast amount of flavours from around the world.</p>
                <p><a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Cuisine" class="link-dark">Click here</a> to find out more about the cuisines available.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                <h2 class="niconne niconne-centre">Dishes</h2>
                <p class="text-white">With a great amount of cuisines comes a great amount of dishes!</p>
                <p><a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Dishes" class="link-dark">Click here</a> to look for a dish.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                <h2 class="niconne niconne-centre">Price</h2>
                <p class="text-white">Whether you're after a super cheap meal or want to treat yourself to something a little more fancy, Canberra has it all.</p>
                <p><a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Price" class="link-dark">Click here</a> to see what's available in your price range.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                <h2 class="niconne niconne-centre">Location</h2>
                <p class="text-white">There might be the perfect meal waiting just around the corner from you. Check out our locations page to find a restaurant near you!</p>
                <p><a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Location" class="link-dark">Click here</a> to see what's available near you.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!--Review Stuff-->

        <section class="row row-white">
            <div class="col-md-5 col-sm-5 col-xs-12">
                <div class="row" style="padding-top: 25px;">
                    <div class="col-xs-6">
                        <img src="~/images/foodimg3.jpg" class="review-image" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-6">
                        <img src="~/images/foodimg4.jpg" class="review-image" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-1 col-sm-1 col-xs-0"></div>
            <div class="col-md-5 col-sm-5 col-xs-12">
                <p class="niconne niconne-row">Reviews</p>
                <p class="oxygen oxygen-row">Can't Make Up Your Mind?</p>
                <p class="text-black">People from around Australia have already visited these restaurants and have given us their thoughts.</p>
                <p class="text-black">Head over to our <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Reviews">Customer Review Page</a> to find out more.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1" style="margin-top: 50px;">
                    <p class="niconne niconne-row double-line">Featured Restaurants</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-xs-12" style="padding-bottom: 0;">

                    <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" data-interval="6000">
                        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                            <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                            <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                            <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                            <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="3"></li>
                            <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="4"></li>
                            <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="5"></li>
                        </ol>
                        <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
                            <div class="item active">
                                <a href="http://chickengourmet.com.au/">
                                    <img src="~/images/cg2.jpg" alt="Chicken Gourmet" class="img-responsive" />
                                </a>
                                <div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
                                    <p>Chicken Gourmet</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="item">
                                <a href="http://chakichaki.com.au/">
                                    <img src="~/images/chaki2.jpg" alt="Chaki Chaki" class="img-responsive" />
                                </a>
                                <div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
                                    <p>Chaki Chaki</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="item">
                                <a href="http://www.ciscosmexicano.com.au/">
                                    <img src="~/images/cisco1.jpg" alt="Cisco's Restaurante Mexicano" class="img-responsive" />
                                </a>
                                <div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
                                    <p>Cisco's Restaurante Mexicano</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="item">
                                <a href="http://iori.com.au/">
                                    <img src="~/images/iori1.jpeg" alt="Iori" class="img-responsive" />
                                </a>
                                <div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
                                    <p>Iori</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="item">
                                <a href="http://misterzees.com.au/">
                                    <img src="~/images/mz2.jpg" alt="Mister Zee's" class="img-responsive" />
                                </a>
                                <div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
                                    <p>Mister Zee's</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="item">
                                <a href="http://www.sagerestaurant.net.au/">
                                    <img src="~/images/sage3.jpg" alt="Sage" class="img-responsive" />
                                </a>
                                <div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
                                    <p>Sage</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                        </a>
                        <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
                            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>


        </section>

    </div>
</div>